divs: Sighting DetailsWalking towards the East and taking pictures with a Sony DSC camera of a cloud formation to the South. After veiwing the photos on my computer monitor I realized that one of several shots, which were taken very rapidly as I was walking, contained the anomally which can be seen in the lower center of the photo. Comments, questions and explanations welcome.
